{
  "stem": "13382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew that father was, at that time, at the railway station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, news goes fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, you know, Budapest is not so large.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother face and everything-- you know, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just thought, I mean, they will let them out or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we've been waiting for some sort of a sign of the father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two days later, a Hungarian elderly policeman, who was a guard in that detention camp-- quite looked quite decent and sort of sympathetic-- he brought a letter from our father.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the father wrote, and that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked, you know, certain things-- for [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH] and-- and underwear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, you know-- so that policeman became a contact for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I mean, he's doing it for money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had quite a few contact with father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, my mother would send him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, he wasn't eating any [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He [? served ?] kosher food and-- and then, two weeks later or something, we got a letter from father-- so much enthusiasm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Always the policeman brought to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to pay the money [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he was said, if we would send a large suitcase with the policeman to pack the things, because during that time so many things accumulated, right, because he's coming home.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But he didn't come home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So that was first shipment from Hungary went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they all went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I had to support my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm getting a bit sort of soft now, but I was really strong, all the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never-- never cried, or never a tear came out of my eyes-- just to do something, to save.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
